Affirmative Vote:By voting a feedback item as "Affirmative":
<ul>
<li>You are asserting that, while you would like the item addressed, you are comfortable with the specification proceeding to publication if this item is not addressed immediately or as requested.</li>
<li>You understand this will cause your overall vote on the specification to be set to "Affirmative" unless you have made (or do make) negative comments.  If your vote was previously set to be the "same as" another voter, that link will be removed.</li>
</ul>
